summary: The Loriliard Research Center is located in Greensboro, North Carolina. The study was conducted between March 20, 1965 and March 30, 1985. It was published in the Journal of the American Society for Rats. For confidential support call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 1-800-273-8255 or visit http://www.suicidepreventionlifeline.org/.
